project_descr: The project  is designed to deliver effective assistance to support Armenian stakeholders in improving the electoral process in line with the government’s commitment to organize credible and inclusive elections

outputs.output_descr: Support to the Electoral Process contributes to reinforcement of democratic principles and institutions through introduction of new technology for identification of voters, increasing credible electoral processes and promoting voter participation.
donor_name: UNITED STATES AGENCY FOR INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT (USAID)

document_name: Audio-visual production on new voting technologies and procedures as well as for motivating the Armenian citizens to actively participate in elections
project_title: support to the electoral process in armenia (sepa)
